The measure `WignerMeasure μ ν n` is `Measure.pi (fun (p : Index n) => if p.val.1 = p.val.2 then ν else μ)`. The function `fun ω => wignerMatrixEntryFunction ω i i` is the i-th coordinate function on the sample space `WignerSpace n`. The i-th coordinate function is ν distributed by the definition of the product measure.

