The definition of `wignerMatrixMap` is `fun (ω : WignerSpace n) ↦ (wignerMatrixMap' ω)`, where `wignerMatrixMap'` is `Matrix.of (wignerMatrixEntryFunction ω)`. The entry at (i,i) is `wignerMatrixEntryFunction ω i i`.

